################################################################################
  UNJYNX - SCREENSHOT SPECIFICATION
  Version: 1.0.0
  Last Updated: 2026-03-11
################################################################################

================================================================================
  OVERVIEW
================================================================================

  6 screenshots per store listing, optimized for three device classes.
  All screenshots use UNJYNX brand styling: midnight purple background (#0F0A1A),
  electric gold accents (#FFD700), brand violet (#6C5CE7), and purple-mist text
  (#F8F5FF).

  Typography: Bebas Neue for headlines, Outfit for body text, DM Sans for UI.

================================================================================
  DEVICE FRAMES & DIMENSIONS
================================================================================

  GOOGLE PLAY STORE:
  - Pixel 8 Pro:      1344 x 2992 px (6.7" display, required flagship)
  - 7" Tablet:        1200 x 1920 px (optional but recommended)
  - 10" Tablet:       1600 x 2560 px (optional)

  APPLE APP STORE:
  - iPhone 15 Pro Max: 1290 x 2796 px (6.7" Super Retina XDR, REQUIRED)
  - iPhone 8 Plus:     1242 x 2208 px (5.5" Retina HD, REQUIRED)
  - iPad Pro 12.9":    2048 x 2732 px (optional)

  FILE FORMAT:
  - PNG or JPEG, sRGB color space
  - No transparency (App Store rejects it)
  - No device bezels in the image for App Store (Apple adds them)
  - Google Play allows device frames in screenshots

================================================================================
  GLOBAL DESIGN RULES
================================================================================

  BACKGROUND:
  - Solid gradient from #0F0A1A (top) to #1A0F2E (bottom)
  - Subtle radial glow behind device frame: violet (#6C5CE7) at 8% opacity
  - Optional: floating orbs (violet/gold, blurred) for depth

  TEXT OVERLAYS:
  - Headline: Bebas Neue, 72-96pt, #F8F5FF (purple-mist)
  - Subheadline: Outfit, 36-48pt, #FFD700 (gold) or #F8F5FF at 60% opacity
  - Position: above or below device frame, never overlapping UI
  - Max 6 words per headline, 10 words per subheadline

  DEVICE FRAME:
  - Slight 5-degree tilt for dynamism (optional, keep consistent across set)
  - Drop shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.15)
  - Device frame color: space black for all devices

  BRANDING:
  - UNJYNX logo watermark in bottom-right corner, 60% opacity, small
  - Gold accent line (2px) at top of each screenshot

================================================================================
  SCREENSHOT 1: HOME SCREEN + PROGRESS RINGS
================================================================================

  SCREEN SHOWN:
  Home screen (C1) displaying:
  - "Good morning, [Name]" greeting with date
  - Today's task list (3-4 tasks visible, one completed with strikethrough)
  - Progress rings in top-right: daily completion %, streak count
  - Bottom navigation bar visible

  APP STATE:
  - Dark theme active
  - 3 of 5 tasks completed (60% ring filled)
  - 12-day streak badge glowing gold
  - One task marked urgent (gold border)

  TEXT OVERLAY:
  Headline:    "YOUR DAY. ORGANIZED."
  Subheadline: "Track tasks and streaks at a glance."

  NOTES:
  - This is the first screenshot users see -- it must communicate "task manager"
    instantly while hinting at the progress/gamification angle
  - Show realistic task names (e.g., "Review Q1 report", "Call dentist",
    "Push feature branch")

================================================================================
  SCREENSHOT 2: MULTI-CHANNEL REMINDERS
================================================================================

  SCREEN SHOWN:
  Channel selection screen (J2) or notification preferences showing:
  - List of 7 channel tiles: WhatsApp (green), Telegram (blue),
    Instagram (pink), SMS (gold), Discord (indigo), Slack (purple), Email (violet)
  - Each tile shows: channel icon, name, toggle switch (some ON, some OFF)
  - At least 3 channels toggled ON with checkmarks
  - Escalation chain preview at bottom: "WhatsApp -> SMS -> Email"

  APP STATE:
  - WhatsApp: connected (green dot)
  - Telegram: connected (blue dot)
  - SMS: connected (gold dot)
  - Others: available but not connected (dimmed)

  TEXT OVERLAY:
  Headline:    "REMINDERS. EVERYWHERE."
  Subheadline: "WhatsApp. Telegram. Instagram. SMS. 7 channels."

  NOTES:
  - Channel icons should use their official brand colors
  - The escalation chain visual is a key differentiator -- make it prominent
  - Consider showing a WhatsApp message bubble mockup floating beside the phone

================================================================================
  SCREENSHOT 3: GHOST MODE + FOCUS TIMER
================================================================================

  SCREEN SHOWN:
  Ghost Mode screen (G1) displaying:
  - Large circular Pomodoro timer (25:00 or mid-session like 18:32)
  - "GHOST MODE ACTIVE" badge at top
  - Ambient sound selector showing current sound (e.g., "Rain" with waveform)
  - Session stats: "Focus: 2h 15m today"
  - Subtle ghost/invisible effect on background (translucent overlay)

  APP STATE:
  - Timer running at 18:32
  - Rain ambient sound active (waveform animation implied)
  - Dark theme with extra-dim background (Ghost Mode overlay)
  - Gold timer ring with progress arc

  TEXT OVERLAY:
  Headline:    "LOCK IN. GO GHOST."
  Subheadline: "Deep focus with Pomodoro + ambient sounds."

  NOTES:
  - The ghost/stealth aesthetic should feel premium and mysterious
  - Timer ring should be the dominant visual element
  - Ambient sound selector is a unique touch -- make sure it is visible
  - Consider a subtle "apps blocked" indicator

================================================================================
  SCREENSHOT 4: PROGRESS HUB
================================================================================

  SCREEN SHOWN:
  Progress Hub screen (I1) displaying:
  - Three concentric completion rings (daily, weekly, monthly) -- Strava-style
  - Contribution heatmap grid (GitHub-style, purple-to-gold color scale)
  - Current streak: "47 days" with fire icon
  - Personal best badge: "Longest streak: 47 days"
  - Weekly insight card: "You complete 40% more tasks on Tuesdays"

  APP STATE:
  - Impressive streak number (47 days)
  - Heatmap showing consistent activity over 3+ months
  - All three rings nearly full (85%+)
  - Weekly insight visible

  TEXT OVERLAY:
  Headline:    "TRACK YOUR STREAK."
  Subheadline: "Heatmaps, rings, and personal bests."

  NOTES:
  - The heatmap and rings should feel like a fitness app dashboard
  - Use purple-to-gold gradient for heatmap cells (cold to hot)
  - Streak number should be large and gold
  - This screenshot sells the gamification angle

================================================================================
